	- with random { rrand(0,1) }!8
	- with osc or lfnoise
- osc an argument (with different freq for each for phasing pseudo random effect or tempo frequence for rhytm)
- lfnoise an argument
- fm an argument ( 1 + ( SinOsc.kr(fm) * 1 ))


